{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20171.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800102,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-1"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So...um...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-2"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Thank you so much for rescuing me today!"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Don't worry about it.@It's my duty as a Magical Girl."},{"chara":[{"id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-4"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Are you always fighting Witches like that?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes. What might appear to be natural@disasters or accidents through the@eyes of regular people..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...are often caused by Witches and@their minions."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You can see Witches, as well as me.@That means you have the potential@to become a Magical Girl."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-8"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The potential...to become a Magical Girl?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If you make a contract with me,@you'll be able to fight Witches like Mami."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-10"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But, I...@I don't think I have it in me."},{"chara":[{"id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-11"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm not suited for that kind of thing...@I'm not brave enough..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It certainly does come with risks.@So, I won't force you into it."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyubey","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But by making a contract, you'll be@granted one wish in exchange."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-14"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]A wish...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's right."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Not everyone has the potential@to make a contract..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, why not think on it for a bit?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800102,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-18"}],"nameAvRight":"","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200501,"pos":0}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200903,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"flashEffect":"explosion","surround":"8065_opticalcamouflage"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She was really torn about it, huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's understandably difficult to make@a decision after being told something@like this out of the blue."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But, if there's a wish she wants@to realize..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Then it could be a good chance@to fulfill it."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Also, there's been a slight uptick@in Witch presence lately."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Even if we have my foresight, there's@a limit to what the two of us can handle."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-25"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]We can always use some more allies...right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-26"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well... That's only if we can all@stay on the same page."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Should I go and look into the future?"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Figure out what her desire is,@how to convince her and all that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It should be useful in nudging her@to decide."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-30"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"lipSynch":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]All right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Go ahead, Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-33"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes ma'am.@Then, let me take a look..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"white","bgm":"stop","item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/film13_mami_seriously.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"white","deleteArmatureList":[1],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.1},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.01,"surround":"8005_heartbeat"},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":2,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/1509_prophecy_active.ExportJson","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"autoTurnLast":0.01},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_20171.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":0.2},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":300,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-34"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm...I see, I see.@This might be a bit difficult to bring up.","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200900}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-35","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-34"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]How so?"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-36"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Apparently, her wish is simple:@\"To become rich!\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":200}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-37","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-36"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's like...a really straightforward desire,@isn't it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-39"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But don't worry."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-40"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]After she says that, if you share the@reason why you made a contract..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-002-41"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She'll open up to you, and make@her decision."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
